      "title": "<span id=\"#28228\" class=\"scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold flex items-center\"><h1 class=\"inline !mb-1 scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold\">clockwise</h1><div class=\"pl-2 flex-1 text-textSecondary text-xl font-serif\">(adv.)</div></span>",
      "html": "<p>也就是 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">clock-wise</i>，意思是“顺时针方向”，起源于1879年，由 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of clock \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/clock\">clock</a>（n.1）和 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of wise \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/wise\">wise</a>（n.）组成。</p>"
